Achievements.Name: Meet Mick
Achievements.Description: You've met Mick. He knows a lot about fighting. You feel a connection between the two of you.

Achievements.Name: Meet Apu
Achievements.Description: You've met Apu. He's a shop owner. Does he ever sleep?

Achievements.Name: Meet Tyler
Achievements.Description: You've met Tyler. He looks like a good guy. I think you should spend more time with him.

Achievements.Name: Meet Silver
Achievements.Description: You've met Silver. He seems arrogant. I hope he'll teach you something.

Achievements.Name: Meet Casey
Achievements.Description: You've met Casey. He used to be a sailor. Now he can be your employer. I think he is dangerous.

Achievements.Name: Prevention of a crime
Achievements.Description: You prevented a crime for the first time. I am proud of you!

Achievements.Name: Pizza eater
Achievements.Description: It tastes good. I see that you like it. But you should probably eat healthier food.

Achievements.Name: Spicy pizza
Achievements.Description: Mmm... it's so tasty and spicy. I hope I'll try it someday.

Achievements.Name: Beat Bill
Achievements.Description: It was hard, but you kicked that green ass.

Achievements.Name: Beat Mark
Achievements.Description: Wow, his staff was really dangerous. But you've won! I could get used to that.

Achievements.Name: Beat Gabe
Achievements.Description: Passed...Would I be so lucky.

Achievements.Name: Beat Steve
Achievements.Description: Done! You really did it! Can I call you Dundee now?

Achievements.Name: 5th Place
Achievements.Description: You've just taken 5th place in the league. Keep going!

Achievements.Name: Street fighter
Achievements.Description: You did it! You've won 5 times. I always believed in you!

Achievements.Name: First fight
Achievements.Description: Hm... you've just finished your first fight. Now you feel strange.

Achievements.Name: Training results
Achievements.Description: Now your shape is better than ever! You look even better than me.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate fights
Achievements.Description: Now you can fight in the ultimate league. I am a little worried about possible injuries.

Achievements.Name: Take the challenge
Achievements.Description: The first bloody fight - done!

Achievements.Name: Ready to challenge
Achievements.Description: Yellow zone - done! Oh my.. I think it's getting really tough now.

Achievements.Name: rime Fighter
Achievements.Description: You've proven yourself as a true defender of your wallet! I think all criminals will avoid you now.

Achievements.Name: Trouble in Little China
Achievements.Description: There is no more trouble in Little China. No more chinese food for me.

Achievements.Name: Big Bobo
Achievements.Description: You've met Bobo. And you know what.. for the first time I have to admit that I was wrong.

Achievements.Name: The Don
Achievements.Description: You've met the Don. I can't even imagine how powerful he is.

Achievements.Name: The mobster
Achievements.Description: Now you're a part of Bobos gang! May I call you little Bobo now?

Achievements.Name: Mickey
Achievements.Description: You've met Tyler's brother. He seems like a good guy.

Achievements.Name: The silence
Achievements.Description: The neighborhood has become so peaceful and calm. But I still won't live here.

Achievements.Name: Professional Multi Card
Achievements.Description: The card is yours! Now we can earn money with your fists!

Achievements.Name: The Sound of Music
Achievements.Description: Bobo looks happy as child with his new hearing aid. I hope that he stops shouting now.

Achievements.Name: Triple B
Achievements.Description: You've beaten Big Bob! He doesn't need your clothes anymore. Now he needs some new teeth!

Achievements.Name: Prison Fight
Achievements.Description: Everything is arranged except for your pillow.

Achievements.Name: King of the Hill
Achievements.Description: Crime - prison - kick some ass - freedom !

Achievements.Name: Beat Ivangief
Achievements.Description: You've avenged your friend! And got the medallion back! Now you can return home.

Achievements.Name: The Medallion
Achievements.Description: You got the medallion! No strange power yet. Have you tried rubbing it?

Achievements.Name: The Island
Achievements.Description: You've done it! One last step before you face the Man in black.

Achievements.Name: The Champion
Achievements.Description: You are the World Champion now.

Achievements.Name: A friend
Achievements.Description: Roy is a good guy. You could really become friends.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Champion
Achievements.Description: Now you are the Ultimate champion!

Achievements.Name: 300 days
Achievements.Description: Beat the game in 300 days.

Achievements.Name: 200 Days
Achievements.Description: Beat the game in 200 days.

Achievements.Name: Hardcore
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the hardcore difficulty

Achievements.Name: The Dark Fist
Achievements.Description: Now you are the Dark Fist! You're so cool.

Achievements.Name: The Power Armor
Achievements.Description: Now you have full power armor. You look tough!

Achievements.Name: The best of brothers
Achievements.Description: You've proved that you are better fighter than your brother.

Achievements.Name: Ninja slayer
Achievements.Description: Ninja slayer

Achievements.Name: 100 Days
Achievements.Description: Beat the game in 100 days.

Achievements.Name: Avenge Fluffy!
Achievements.Description: Hmmm... Turns out Fluffy is kind of a douche.

Achievements.Name: You need to save Fluffy!
Achievements.Description: Hmm... Actually, you didn't save Fluffy.
